snippet.title: Unread Messages Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the demo on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2551940

Unread Messages is a retro-inspired cyberpunk puzzle game where you deliver texts by making connections between cell towers. Alongside your AI companion, FASMA, solve confounding levels and uncover the secrets hidden within Simullect Inc's computers.

Follow me on Twitter!
https://twitter.com/PastelPixelsDev
